### Keybindings
## Remove some stupid / dangerous key bindings
bind k
bind ^k
bind .
bind ^\
bind \\
bind ^h
bind h

## I hate this in emacs:
bind ^g

## Make them better
bind 'Q' quit
bind 'K' kill
bind 'I' login on
bind 'O' login off
bind '}' history
bind 'o' only

### Options

## No startup message thank you very much
startup_message off

## Visual bell overrides the lovely beeping
vbell off

## Changed C-a to C-\ since C-a is like the most used binding ever
escape ^|\

## XON/XOFF ruins my day
stty -ixon

## Some startup windows:
screen -t editor 0 $SHELL
screen -t local 1 $SHELL
screen -t remote 2 $SHELL

#screen -t emacs 9 emacs -nw
#screen -t irssi 9 irssi


